Package edu.phema.elm_to_omop.vocabulary.phema

Class PhemaConceptSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ohdsi.circe.cohortdefinition.ConceptSet
      • edu.phema.elm_to_omop.vocabulary.phema.PhemaConceptSet
  • public class PhemaConceptSet
extends org.ohdsi.circe.cohortdefinition.ConceptSet
    Wrapper around the Circe ConceptSet class that adds a reference to the valuset OID, which is necessary when translating Retrieve expressions.

    We would potentially use OID as the ConceptSet name, which would obviate the need for this class.
